Elliott Candidate on National Express Shortlist, Telegraph Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-04T22:35:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/elliott-candidate-on-national-express-shortlist-telegraph-says.html
National Express Group Plc (NEX)  has placed
Chris Muntwyler, one of three candidates proposed by activist
investor Elliott Advisors (UK) Ltd., on a short list of six
names from which two or three non-executive directors will be
selected, the  Daily Telegraph  reported, without saying where it
got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 